#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:2
msgid "Quantum Reservoirs"
msgstr "Reservorios Cuánticos"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.QuantumReservoir` "
"functional executes a reservoir pipeline over a sequence of inputs. Each "
"layer applies an optional pre-processing circuit, an analog reservoir "
"dynamics block (:class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`), and an "
"optional post-processing circuit, followed by measurements of one or more"
" observables. The optional ``qubits_to_reset`` list can be used to reset "
"selected qubits between layers."
msgstr ""
"El funcional :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.QuantumReservoir` "
"ejecuta un pipeline de reservoir sobre una secuencia de entradas. Cada "
"capa aplica un circuito de preprocesamiento opcional, un bloque de "
"dinámica de reservoir analog (:class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`), "
"y un circuito de postprocesamiento opcional, seguido de mediciones de uno "
"o más observables. La lista opcional ``qubits_to_reset`` puede utilizarse "
"para restablecer qubits seleccionados entre capas."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:9
msgid ""
"The reservoir inputs are represented using "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput` "
"parameters. These behave like standard "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Parameter` objects but are marked as non-"
"trainable so they can be driven by input data sequences rather than "
"optimization loops."
msgstr ""
"Las entradas del reservoir se representan mediante parámetros "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput`. Estos se "
"comportan como objetos :class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Parameter` "
"estándar, pero están marcados como no entrenables para que puedan ser "
"dirigidos por secuencias de datos de entrada en lugar de bucles de "
"optimización."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:13
msgid "**Parameters**"
msgstr "**Parámetros**"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:15
msgid ""
"**initial_state** (:class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`): Initial state"
" of the reservoir."
msgstr ""
"**initial_state** (:class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`): Estado inicial "
"del reservoir."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:16
msgid ""
"**reservoir_layer** "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirLayer`): "
"Defines pre/post-processing, reservoir dynamics, observables, and reset "
"policy."
msgstr ""
"**reservoir_layer** "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirLayer`): "
"Define el preprocesamiento/postprocesamiento, la dinámica del reservoir, "
"los observables y la política de restablecimiento."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:18
msgid ""
"**input_per_layer** (List[Dict[str, float]]): Input values to apply at "
"each layer, keyed by input parameter names (typically the labels of "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput`)."
msgstr ""
"**input_per_layer** (List[Dict[str, float]]): Valores de entrada a "
"aplicar en cada capa, indexados por nombres de parámetros de entrada "
"(normalmente las etiquetas de "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput`)."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:21
msgid "**Returns**"
msgstr "**Retorna**"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:23
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`: Access "
"per-layer expectation values via "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_expectation_values`,"
" plus optional states via "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_intermediate_states`"
" if state tomography was requested in the readout spec."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`: Accede "
"a los valores esperados por capa mediante "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_expectation_values`,"
" más estados opcionales mediante "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_intermediate_states`"
" si se solicitó tomografía de estado en la especificación de lectura."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:28
msgid "Usage Example"
msgstr "Ejemplo de Uso"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:71
msgid "Encoding Input Data"
msgstr "Codificación de Datos de Entrada"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_reservoirs.rst:73
msgid ""
"You can inject classical data into a reservoir layer in multiple places. "
"The only requirement is that the keys in ``input_per_layer`` match the "
"labels of the "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput` objects "
"you place in the layer."
msgstr ""
"Se pueden inyectar datos clásicos en una capa del reservoir en múltiples "
"lugares. El único requisito es que las claves en ``input_per_layer`` "
"coincidan con las etiquetas de los objetos "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput` que se "
"colocan en la capa."

